A scorpion chain is a weapon developed and used by the [[Vulkoori]] [[drow]] of [[Xen'drik]]. It is a spiked chain with a daggerlike blade at each end. The drow have perfected the use of the weapon to harass larger enemies such as [[giant]]s, or as a poison-delivery weapon against less hardy foes.